<!-- login.component.html -->
<form>
    <mat-form-field>
      <input matInput placeholder="Usuario" name="username">
    </mat-form-field>
    <mat-form-field>
      <input matInput type="password" placeholder="Contraseña" name="password">
    </mat-form-field>
    <button mat-raised-button color="primary">Iniciar sesión</button>
  </form>
